export default function AboutMe() { return (

About

About Me

Hello, I'm Jay R Gueta Santos, a recent graduate with a degree in BS Computer Science. Throughout my academic journey at Cavite State University-CCAT Campus, I maintained a consistent presence on the Dean's List. I embody an outgoing personality, making it easy for me to connect with others and remain approachable. My collaborative nature as a team player has allowed me to contribute effectively and continuously strive for personal growth.

In terms of my skillset, I am knowledgeable in various programming languages and technologies. I'm well-versed in C++, VB.NET, Python, JavaScript, React.js, Node.js, PHP, and MySQL. These skills have equipped me to approach diverse challenges and deliver innovative solutions. I am enthusiastic about learning and adapting to new technologies to further enhance my abilities.
